name: MINTED MAG ISSUE #1 - PURCHASE TOKEN
description:
Receive the MINTED MAG Issue #1 zine airdropped into your TEZ wallet with the purchase of this NFT.

Minted Mag is born on the blockchain. A monthly zine publication created by artists for artists, Minted Mag offers the opportunity for artists to submit their NFTs to be featured in a curated magazine. The zine is then minted on the hic et nunc platform, with all proceeds going back to support the growth of MINTED MAG.

*All copies will be sent to the wallet address which purchased this token on the 31st of August*

Twit - @mintedmag
